title: Microsoft Azure Virtual Machine: Burst CPU Credits
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check provides information about VM CPU burst credits in
 the Microsoft Azure cloud.
 The number of consumed and remaining credits is displayed.

 The thresholds for CPU remaining credits can be configured using the rule
 "Azure VM Burst CPU Credits".

discovery:
 One service is created on every VM host. The option
 "Map data to the VM itself" has to be configured in the Azure agent.
